Third Department,

June, 1957

(June 13, 1957) In the Matter of the Claim of Harry Albee, Appellant, against Buffalo Evening News et al., Respondents. Workmen’s Compensation Board, Respondent.

Motion to dismiss appeal granted, by default, without costs. Present — Foster, P. J., Bergan, Coon, Halpern and Gibson, JJ.
